reviewText: great set for a big fan.

Zuffa has stopped producing DVD's for UFC events in America (UFC 186) so we are stuck with these more expensive ones produced by a company called Beyond Entertainment in Australia. This is a good deal if you are wanting some of the more recent events especially 193 - Rousey vs Holm and UFC 187 Johnson vs. Cormier. I'm disappointed that they stopped producing the DVD's but at least we have this option I guess.
